data.description: Rarely Offered Briarcliff, Quiet Country living situated minutes from Beaches, Shopping, Dining, Hospitals, Airport. This 1.14-acre estate features: a completely remodeled home to include: 4 Bedrooms, a 2nd level Master with bath, dual sinks & multi-head shower, Loft bedroom w/bath, Unique Jack & Jill 1st level bedrooms w/bath, all 3.5 Baths newly remodeled, New flooring throughout with tile and 2nd level Bamboo, What a view off the 2nd level master balcony, Kitchen, Laundry room, & Outside Bar Area have unique designer concrete counter surfaces, 2019 new roof & gutters, Dual Multi Zone ACs & Duct work 2022, Dual Hot Water Tanks 2019, Open Cell Spray Foam Insulation in attic, Resort Style Saltwater Pool & Fenced Designer Paver Patio 2021 with Pentair operational & color App Automation System, Covered large Pavilion, 2022 Well pump, 2nd garage a workshop/golf cart or motorcycles, storage buildings, w/water shed, and if you want a chicken coop complete with chickens. Entire property boasts a mature landscape and long driveway. NO HOA!! The sellers remodeled this property for themselves, but a transfer has made them give up their dream home. Every item of remodel was done with LOVE!
